### System Addad ###

. System Dah Dahi (Decimal)

exp.
1234 = 4(1) + 3(10) + 2(100) + 1(1000)

. System Hast HAshti (Octal)

exp.
134(OCT) = 4(8^0) + 3(8^1) + 1(8^2)

. System Shanzdah Shanzdahi (HexaDecimal)

exp.
115(HEX) = 1F(HEX)

### NOTE ###
# 10 A     #
# 11 B     #
# 12 C     #
# 13 D     #
# 14 E     #
# 15 F     #
############

. System Do Doi (Binary)

### NOTE #########
#                #
# Zaban Computer #
#                #
##################

### Tabdilat dar system addad ###

OCT ==> DECIMAL ==>
Ragham ha ra az samt rast ba tavajoh be moghiat (i) ra dar
(8^i) zarb mikonim va hasel ha ra ba ham jam mikonim

