# Rah hal Baghi Mande ha #

# Rah hal Tavan ha #

### Anva Dade ha : ###

. Dade Sahih

exp.
0,1,2,3,...

. Dade Ashari

exp.
1.1,1.2,1.3

. Dade Characteri

exp.
a,b,c,...

### Moteghiar (Variable) ###

yek makan movaghat ke yek no dade dar khod zakhire mikonad

### Anva Amalgar ha ###

. jam
. zarb
. menha(Tafrigh) ==> 1 - Tafrigh Yekani
. Taghsim ==> 1 - Taghsim sahih ; 2 - Taghsim Ashari
. Tavan
. Baghimane (mod)

## Amalgar manteghi ##

. Boolean ==> True or False
. or ==> |
. And ==> &
. Not ==> Naghiz ==> (!)

## Amalgar haye Moghaiesee ##

. >
. <
. =>
. =<
. ==
. !=

exp.
x = 2
(x mod(2) = 0)


### Olaviat Ha ###

. Tafrigh Yekani
. Tavan
. Zarb va Taghsim
. Jam va Tafrigh

# Baraye be ham zadan olaviat az () estefade mishavad #

### Amaliat haye riazi ###

. Factorial :
  n! = (n)(n-1)(n-2)(n-3)...(1)

. Tarkibiat:
   k
  C = n!/k!(n-k)!
   n

## Amaliat matris ha ##

1 - Jam va Tafrigh : Deraye haye nazir be nazir ra ba ham jam ya tafrigh mikonim.
2 - Zarb matris ha : 
3 - Mohasebe Determinan : 
  A = | a b |
      | c d |

det(A) = |A| = 
. (a * d) - (b * c)
. Saroos Method ==> (Badihi ast)

4 - Mohasebe Taranahad ==> Jaye Satr va Sotoon deraye ha avaz mishavad
5 - Mohasebe Matris Bala Mosalasi va paeen Mosalasi

### Algorithm & Flowchart ###

## Marahel Hal Masele ##

. Moshakhas nemoodan vooroodi
. Moshakhas nemoodan Khorooji
. Pardazesh vooroodi ha va ijad khoorooji khaste shode

## Tarif Algorithm ##

. Majmooee az dastoorat ke har dastoor deraye yek shomare ast va ejraye an ha (ba yek tartib moshakhas) 
  monjar be anjam yek kar khas mishavad, algorithm gofte mishavad.

## Vijegi haye barez algorithm ##

. Daraye noghte shroo va payan ast.
. Tedad dastoorat dar anha motenahi va moshakhas ast.
. Ejraye dastoorat elzaman be tartib nist, va tabe mohtavaye dastoorat ast.

## Anva Dastoor amal ha dar algorithm ##

. Dastoor Vooroodi
. Dastoor Khorooji
. Dastoor Entesab
. Dastoor Mohasebati va Manteghi
. Dastoor Tasmim Giri
. Tozihat

### Sakhtar haye Tekrar ###

. Sakhtar hayee ba tekrar moshakhas
==> az abteda tekrar amal moshakhas ast

. Sakhtar hayee ba tekrar namoshakhas
==> tedad tekrar Vabaste be sharayet dade haye vooroodi va sharayet masele khahad bood

       ----------
      |          |
      v          |
 ----------      |
|          |     |
|   loop   |     |
|          |     |
 ----------      |
      |          |
      v----------
    shart khateme

## Halghe haye tekrar moshakhas ==> (for) ##

1 - Halghe haye soodi (bala shomar)
2 - Halghe haye noozooli (paeen shomar)

### ### ### ### ###

exp. Algorithmi benevisid ke hasel ebarat zir ra mohasebe konad.

a. S = 1 + 1/2 + 1/4 + ... + 1/2n

b. S = 2 + 3/2! + 4/3! + ... + n+1/n!

c. S(x) = x - (x^3)/3! + (x^5)/5! + ... +|- (x^2k-1)/(2k-1)!

==> Sol.

a. 
   1 - Start
   2 - n ra az vooroodi bgir
   3 - I = 1
   4 - S = 1
   5 - S = S + 1/2I
   6 - I = I + 1
   7 - if I <= n goto 5
   8 - print(S)
   9 - End

b.
   1 - Start
   2 - n ra az vooroodi
   3 - I = 1 , S = 0
   4 - F = 1 , temp = I
   5 - F = F * temp
   6 - temp = temp - 1
   7 - if temp > 0 goto 5
   8 - S = S + (I + 1)/temp
   9 - I = I + 1
   10 - if I <= n goto 4
   11 - print(S)
   12 - End

c.
   1 - Start
   2 - K , X ra az vooroodi begir
   3 - S = 0 , I = 1 , sign = 1
   
   ### (X ^ I)/I!         |
   4 - null = 1 , J = 1   |
   5 - null = null * X    | ==> (X ^ I)
   6 - J = J + 1          |
   7 - if J <= I goto 5   |
   
   8 - F = 1 , J = 1      |
   9 - F = F * J          | ==> (I!)
   10 - J = J + 1         |
   11 - if J <= I goto 9  |
   
   12 - S = S + (sign * null/F)
   13 - Sign = - Sign
   14 - I = I = 2
   15 - if I <= 2k-1 then goto 4
   16 - End

## Halghe haye tekrar to dar to ##

exp. ==> In previous exp. Section b

### Note ################################
#                                       #
# be ezaye har bar ejraye halghe birooni#
# halghe dakheli an kamel ejra mishavad #
#                                       #
#########################################

exp.
     algorithmi benevisid ke shekl zir ra chap konad.

#### A #####
#          #
#   *      #
#   **     #
#   ***    #
#   ****   #
#   *****  #
#   ****** #
#   .      #
#   .      #
#   .      #
############

Sol(A).
        1 - Shroo
        2 - n ra az vooroodi begir
        3 - I = 1
        4 - J = 1
        5 - Dar hamin satr yek "*" chap kon
        6 - J = J + 1
        7 - if J <= I goto 5
        8 - Makan nama ra yek satr paeen bebar => Works like "Enter"
        9 - I = I + 1
        10 - if I <= n goto 4

#### B #######
#            #
#   *****    #
#   ****     #
#   ***      #
#   **       #
#   *        #
#   *        #
#   **       #
#   ***      #
#   ****     #
#   *****    #
#            #
##############

Sol(B).
        1 - Start
        2 - I = 5
        3 - J = 1
        4 - Dar hamin satr yek "*" chap kon
        5 - J = J + 1
        6 - if J <= I goto 4
        7 - Makan nama ra be satr badi bebar
        8 - I = I - 1
        9 - if I > 0 goto 3
        10 - I = I + 1
        11 - J = 1
        12 - Dar hamin satr yek "*" chap kon
        13 - J = J + 1
        14 - if J <= 1 goto 12
        15 - if I <= 5 goto 10
        16 - End

exp.
     Algorithmi benevisid ke N ra daryaft konad va addad ghabl az an ra chap konad.

Sol.
     1 - Start
     2 - N ra az vooroodi begir
     3 - test = 2
     4 - I = 2 , f = 0
     5 - if test mod I = 0 then f = 1
     6 - if f = 1then goto 9
     7 -  = I + 1
     8 - if I <= test/2 goto 5
     9 - if f = 0 then print(test)
     10 - test = test + 1
     11 - if test <= n then goto 4
     12 - End

### Flowchart ###

. Tarif : Baraye neshan dadan ravand ejraye yek algorithm , va ejad yek sakhtar graphici az algorithm 
          ke did koli az algorithm baraye binande ejad mikonad az Flowchart estefade mishavad.

## Alaiem dar Flowchart ##

. Shroo & payan : Beizi
. Dastoorat Sharti : Lozi

   /\
  /  \
 /    \
/      \
condition --> True
\      /
 \    /
  \  /
   \/
   |
   | False
   v

. Vooroodi va khoorooji : Motevaziol azla
. Dastoorat Mohasebe va entesab : Mostatil

exp.
     Flowcharti rasm konid ke yek addad az vroodi begirad va moshakhas konad ke moraba kamel ast ya na?

Beizi(Start)
    |
    |
    v
Lozi(Read(n))
    |
    |
    v
Mostatil(S = 0 , I = 1)
    |
    |  <-------------------------------------------
    v                                              |
Mostatil(S = S + I)                                |
    |                                              |
    |                                              |
    v                                              |
Mostatil(I = I + 2)                                |
    |                                              |
    |                                              |
    v                                              |
Lozi(if n = s) -- YES --> Lozi(n kamel ast)        |
    |                                    |         |
    |                                    |         |
    NO                                   |         |
    |                                    |         |
    |                                    |         |
    v                                    |         |
Lozi(if n < s) -- YES -------------------|---------
   |                                     |
   |                                     |
   NO                                    |
   |                                     |
   |                                     |
   v                                     v
Lozi(n kamel nist) -------------> Beizi(End)

exp. 
     Flowcharti rasm konid ; ke n jomle aval seri fibonatchi ra chap konad

Sol.

Beizi(Start)
    |
    |
    v
Motevaziol azla(Read(n))
    |
    |
    v
Mostatil(
a = 0
b = 1
I = 2)
    |
    | <-------------------------
    v                           |
Mostatil(I = I + 1)             |
    |                           |
    |                           |
    v                           |
Mostatil(                       |
c = a + b                       |
a = b                           |
b = c)                          |
    |                           |
    |                           |
    v                           |
Motevaziol azla(out(c))         |
    |                           |
    |                           |
    v                           |
Lozi(if I < n) ----- YES -------
    |
    |
    NO
    |
    |
    v
    Beizi(End)

exp.
     Flowcharti rasm konid ke n addad az vooroodi daryaft konad va maximum anha va tedad tekrar anha ro moshakhas konad

Sol.

Beizi(Start)
    |
    |
    v
Motevaziol azla(Read(n))
    |
    |
    v
Mostatil(
max = 0
c = 0
i = 1)                     
    |                      
    | <-------------------------------------------
    v                                             |
Motevaziol azla(Read(x))                          |
    |                                             |
    |                                             |
    v                                             |
Lozi(x > max) -- NO --> Mostatil(c = c + 1)       |
    |                          |                  |
    |                          |                  |
    YES                        |                  |
    |                          |                  |
    |                          |                  |
    v                          |                  |
Mostatil(                      |                  |
max = x                        |                  |
c = 1)                         |                  |
    |                          |                  |
     --------------------------                   |
    |                                             |
    |                                             |
    v                                             |
Mostatil(I = I + 1)                               |
   |                                              |
   |                                              |
   v                                              |
Lozi(i <= n) -- YES ------------------------------
   |
   NO
   |
   v
Motevaziol azla(
out(max
out(c))
   |
   |
   v
Beizi(End)

exp.
     agar a addadi bashad ke ba majmoo maghsoom alaihaiash barabar bashad , algorithmi benevisid ke addad a 
     kochek tar az N ra moshakhas konad

Sol.
     1 - Start
     2 - n ra az vooroodi begir
     3 - test = 2
     4 - s = 0
     5 - I = 1
     6 - if test mod I = 0 then S = S + I
     7 - I = I + 1
     8 - if I <= test/2 goto 6
     9 - if test = S then print(S)
     10 - test = test + 1
     11 - if test <= n goto 4
     12 - End

exp.
     Flowcharti rasm konid ; X(^ n) ra mohasebe va chap konad

Sol.
     Beizi(Start)
         |
         |
         v
     Motevaziol azla(n, x ra begir)
         |
         |
         v
     Mostatil(
     i = 1
     F = 1)
         |
         |<-------------------
         v                    |
     Mostatil(F = F * x)      |
         |                    |
         |                    |
         v                    |
     Lozi(if i <= n) -- YES --
         |
         NO
         |
         v
     Lozi(out(F))
         |
         |
         v
     Beizi(End)

exp.
     Flowcharti rasm konid ke bozorg tarin maghsoom alaih moshtarak do addad ra mohasebe va chap konad

Sol.
     Beizi(Start)
        |
        |
        v
     Motevaziol azla(
     Read(x)
     Read(y))
        |
        |<-----------------------
        v                        |
     Lozi(if x < y) ---          |
        |              |         |
        YES            |         |
        |              |         |
        v              NO        |
     Mostatil(         |         |
     temp = x          |         |
     x = y             |         |
     y = temp)         |         |
        |              |         |
        |<-------------          |
        v                        |
     Mostatil(x = x - y)         |
        |                        |
        |                        |
        v                        |
     lozi(if x != y)------ YES --
        |
        |
        v
     Beizi(End)

exp.
     Flowcharti rasm konid ke yek addad dar mabnaye 10 ra be mabnaye 2 bebarad

Sol.
     Beizi(Start)
        |
        |
        v
     Motevaziol azla(Read(x))
        |
        |
        v
     Mostatil(
     S = 0
     i = 0)
        |
        |<--------------------
        v                     |
     Mostatil(                |
     r = x mod 2              |
     x = [x/2])               |
        |                     |
        |                     |
        v                     |
     Mostatil(                |
     S = S + r * 10 ^ i)      |
        |                     |
        |                     |
        v                     |
     Mostatili(               |
     i = i + 1)               |
        |                     |
        |                     |
        v                     |
     lozi(if(x >= 2))-- YES --
        |
        NO
        |
        v
     Mostatil(S = S + x * (10 ^ i))
        |
        |
        v
     Beizi(End)
